short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: A Chrome extension to create a knowledge base from web pages and enable chat interaction.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Discover the power of instant knowledge with SensePage. Say goodbye to time-consuming searches and article scanning. Our interactive chatbot-like interface lets you ask questions and get immediate, tailored responses based on the web page you're browsing. Save precious time and boost productivity with seamless communication and lightning-fast answers. Experience the future of browsing and stay one step ahead. Add SensePage to Chrome now!
